                    <msContents>
                        <summary>President Bush wrote to express support for Chancellor Kohl’s efforts to reunify Germany while remaining in NATO amidst rapidly changing events in Eastern Europe and the Soviet Union.

Also: Memorandum for Brent Scowcroft, 8.2.1990. 
Also: Memorandum for the President.</summary>
